as in clouds that also contribute to the broad line region (BLR)\nemission; and suggest that a geometrically thick neutral gas torus co-exists\nwith the BLR and bridges the gap to the dusty torus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 May 2015 07:06:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-05"}
